## 🔹 Common Interview Question

👉 *“How do you mock network calls in iOS?”*

Answer:

> Use `URLProtocol` to intercept requests and return predefined responses without hitting real APIs.

---

## 🔹 When NOT to use

* Simple apps (overkill)
* When using 3rd-party networking libs that already provide mocking (like Alamofire + plugins)

